<ext_description linkend="Document_properties_arm.document_property_item">
<note>
That extension involves that a <express_ref linkend="document_definition:arm:Document_definition_arm.Document_definition"/> or a <express_ref linkend="file_identification:arm:File_identification_arm.File"/> can be assigned any kind of property.
The purpose of the entity data types defined in the present module is to specify the properties and their representation that are specific to documents and to files.
</note>
</ext_description>

